cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper deals with event detection in videos, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The proposed approach involves a semantic video representation based on tags, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of a simple algorithm, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG).
